print.fRFE Print function for object of class fRFE

#### Description
A print function of an object of class fRFE which is the result of the functions selectFunctional,
selectGroup and selectLevel.

#### Usage
<pre><code>
## S3 method for class 'fRFE'
print(x, ...)
</code></pre>

#### Arguments
* x An object of class fRFE.
* ... optional parameters to be passed to the function ‘summary’.
